WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:02.566
Madam, you are here.

2
00:00:02.666 --> 00:00:03.966
This old thing still offends you

3
00:00:03.966 --> 00:00:05.633
We'll teach him a lesson for you

4
00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:17.500
Shen Guiying, even if you are Zhang Mengjie's biological mother

5
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:19.233
So what?

6
00:00:19.266 --> 00:00:20.700
I'm going to tell Jay

7
00:00:20.866 --> 00:00:22.833
I'm his real mother.

8
00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:25.200
Do you think Xiaojie will listen to you?

9
00:00:26.133 --> 00:00:29.366
It's all you, I could have spared your life

10
00:00:29.366 --> 00:00:31.833
I didn't expect you to recover your memory

11
00:00:32.266 --> 00:00:35.100
You dare to provoke our feelings in front of Oda

12
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:39.233
What do you want to do?

13
00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:43.133
As long as you die

14
00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:46.200
I can completely sit in the position of guarding my mother

15
00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:48.000
Jay will die if you say anything to me

16
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.100
Wait for him to force the rich ship out of the house

17
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:52.466
I'm going to poison him

18
00:00:52.466 --> 00:00:53.366
Is that so?

19
00:00:53.533 --> 00:00:56.966
The property of the Zhang family belongs to me alone

20
00:00:58.400 --> 00:00:59.200
i

21
00:00:59.966 --> 00:01:02.600
I beg you to spare my daughter

22
00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:04.666
I'll give you anything.

23
00:01:05.166 --> 00:01:06.700
Don't be afraid.

24
00:01:07.266 --> 00:01:09.800
I can't possibly miss

25
00:01:11.533 --> 00:01:14.466
You think you're pretending to beg me

26
00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:16.800
Will I punish you easily?

27
00:01:18.900 --> 00:01:20.033
I won.

28
00:01:20.166 --> 00:01:22.633
Besides, I'm determined to wait to unite with you

29
00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:25.466
Even if I die

30
00:01:25.566 --> 00:01:27.666
I won't let you hurt my daughter

